snippet.textDisplay: I remember watching the BTS video for Danah pe Danah by Akhtar Chanal Zehri and Komal Rizvi, and I heard Akhar Sahab say that he was happy that Coke Studio thought about him "Mein sochta tha humein to koi puchta hi nahi..." were his words and those pierced through my heart as I realized how true it was but appreciated Rohail Hyatt's effort to bring him in the mainstream spotlight again. THIS is why I would PREFER having Coke Studio feature the true LEGENDS of music and not some nouveau amateurs like "Mehwish Hayat" trying to debut in Coke Studio. Bring back the legends. Bring people like Akhtar Chanal Zehri and Mithu Tahir back!!! This woman already has the exposure she needs. On the other hand, our legends like Akhtar Sahab are struggling to get some limelight. #bringbackAkhtarChanal #amateurs #cs9 #flop
